labels.shortDescription: Xfleet Query Vehicles for Residual Value Update
labels.value: SELECT Id, Redemption_Price_to_Leasing_Account__c, Current_Month_in_Leasing__c, leasing_Account__r.Leasing_Algorithm__c, Leasing_Rate_Contract__c, Batch_Distribution__c, Leasing_Cost_Per_Month__c, Total_Buy_Price__c, Final_tax_after_deduction__c FROM Vehicle__c WHERE Status__c != 'Sold' AND Current_Month_in_Leasing__c != null AND Leasing_Cost_Per_Month__c != null
